Absolutely—done. I created a quick, clean landing page in **`index.html`** you can use right away:

```html
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>LaunchFlow — Build Faster</title>
  <meta name="description" content="A simple, modern landing page template in pure HTML + CSS." />
  <style>
    :root {
      --bg: #0f172a;
      --bg-soft: #111827;
      --card: #1f2937;
      --text: #e5e7eb;
      --muted: #9ca3af;
      --primary: #6366f1;
      --primary-hover: #4f46e5;
      --accent: #22c55e;
      --maxw: 1100px;
      --radius: 14px;
    }

* { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }

body {
      font-family: Inter, system-ui, -apple-system, Segoe UI, Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
      background: radial-gradient(1200px 500px at 70% -20%, #1d4ed8 0%, transparent 60%), var(--bg);
      color: var(--text);
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

.container {
      width: min(92%, var(--maxw));
      margin: 0 auto;
    }

header {
      padding: 1.25rem 0;
      border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.08);
      backdrop-filter: blur(6px);
      position: sticky;
      top: 0;
      background: rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.75);
    }

.nav {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
    }

.logo {
      font-weight: 700;
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      letter-spacing: .2px;
    }

.nav a {
      color: var(--muted);
      text-decoration: none;
      margin-left: 1rem;
      font-size: .95rem;
    }

.hero {
      padding: 5.5rem 0 4rem;
      text-align: center;
    }

.badge {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: .35rem .75rem;
      border-radius: 999px;
      background: rgba(99,102,241,.15);
      color: #c7d2fe;
      font-size: .82rem;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }

h1 {
      font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 3.2rem);
      line-height: 1.15;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }

.hero p {
      color: var(--muted);
      max-width: 700px;
      margin: 0 auto 1.8rem;
      font-size: 1.05rem;
    }

.cta-group {
      display: flex;
      gap: .8rem;
      justify-content: center;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
    }

.btn {
      padding: .75rem 1.15rem;
      border-radius: 10px;
      border: 1px solid transparent;
      text-decoration: none;
      font-weight: 600;
      font-size: .95rem;
      transition: .2s ease;
    }

.btn-primary {
      background: var(--primary);
      color: #fff;
    }
    .btn-primary:hover { background: var(--primary-hover); }

.btn-secondary {
      border-color: rgba(255,255,255,.18);
      color: var(--text);
      background: rgba(255,255,255,.02);
    }
    .btn-secondary:hover { background: rgba(255,255,255,.06); }

.features {
      padding: 2rem 0 5rem;
    }

.grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
      gap: 1rem;
    }

.card {
      background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(255,255,255,.03), rgba(255,255,255,.01));
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.08);
      border-radius: var(--radius);
      padding: 1.1rem;
    }

.card h3 { margin-bottom: .45rem; font-size: 1.02rem; }
    .card p  { color: var(--muted); font-size: .95rem; }

.dot {
      width: 10px; height: 10px;
      border-radius: 50%;
      background: var(--accent);
      display: inline-block;
      margin-right: .45rem;
    }

.newsletter {
      margin: 0 auto 4rem;
      max-width: 700px;
      background: var(--card);
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.08);
      border-radius: var(--radius);
      padding: 1.2rem;
    }

.newsletter h2 { margin-bottom: .4rem; font-size: 1.3rem; }
    .newsletter p { color: var(--muted); margin-bottom: .9rem; }

form {
      display: flex;
      gap: .6rem;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
    }

input[type="email"] {
      flex: 1 1 260px;
      padding: .75rem .9rem;
      border-radius: 10px;
      border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.14);
      background: #0b1220;
      color: var(--text);
      outline: none;
    }

input[type="email"]:focus {
      border-color: var(--primary);
      box-shadow: 0 0 0 3px rgba(99,102,241,.2);
    }

footer {
      border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.08);
      padding: 1rem 0;
      color: var(--muted);
      text-align: center;
      font-size: .9rem;
    }

@media (max-width: 860px) {
      .grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .hero { padding-top: 4.2rem; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <header>
    <div class="container nav">
      <div class="logo">⚡ LaunchFlow</div>
      <nav>
        <a href="#features">Features</a>
        <a href="#contact">Contact</a>
      </nav>
    </div>
  </header>

<main>
    <section class="hero container">
      <span class="badge">Now in early access</span>
      <h1>Build and launch your next idea in days, not months.</h1>
      <p>
        LaunchFlow gives creators and teams a fast path from concept to live product
        with clean workflows, simple collaboration, and zero busywork.
      </p>
      <div class="cta-group">
        <a href="#" class="btn btn-primary">Get Started Free</a>
        <a href="#features" class="btn btn-secondary">See Features</a>
      </div>
    </section>

<section id="features" class="features container">
      <div class="grid">
        <article class="card">
          <h3><span class="dot"></span>Fast Setup</h3>
          <p>Spin up projects quickly with a clean, no-friction onboarding flow.</p>
        </article>
        <article class="card">
          <h3><span class="dot"></span>Team Friendly</h3>
          <p>Collaborate smoothly with clear tasks, updates, and shared progress.</p>
        </article>
        <article class="card">
          <h3><span class="dot"></span>Built to Scale</h3>
          <p>Start simple, grow confidently—without rebuilding your whole stack.</p>
        </article>
      </div>
    </section>

<section id="contact" class="newsletter container">
      <h2>Stay in the loop</h2>
      <p>Get product updates and launch tips. No spam, unsubscribe anytime.</p>
      <form onsubmit="event.preventDefault(); alert('Thanks for subscribing!');">
        <input type="email" placeholder="Enter your email address" required />
        <button class="btn btn-primary" type="submit">Subscribe</button>
      </form>
    </section>
  </main>

<footer>
    <div class="container">© 2026 LaunchFlow. All rights reserved.</div>
  </footer>
</body>
</html>
```

If you want, I can also make a **business-specific version** (e.g., SaaS, agency, portfolio, product launch) with your brand name/colors in 1 pass.
